===========================================================================

This file contains the main features as well as overviews of specific
bug fixes (and other actions) for each version of the PMI shim since
version 1.0.


1.0.0
------
Initial public release of the PMI shim. Tested against OpenMPI's legacy
PMI-1 and PMI-2 components. Also tested using MPICH head of "main" branch
as of release date for this package.
